    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>竞速平台游戏 &amp; 合作多人模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Git Gud</i> 是一款 **基于技能的竞速平台游戏**，适合单人玩家和合作模式爱好者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你身处一个充满活力的世界，身边唯一的伙伴是一只古怪的鸡，它会不断激励你完成目标，绝不放弃——因为你必须 Git Gud！奔跑、跳跃，挑战高难度关卡，冲击只有极少数人才能达到的排名！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/a9181440fd46d52da87716deaa1ede6c.poster.avif?t=1742134340\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/a9181440fd46d52da87716deaa1ede6c.webm?t=1742134340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/a9181440fd46d52da87716deaa1ede6c.mp4?t=1742134340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解锁最难关卡</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第 4 关:</strong> 需要达到 B+ 评分或更高。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第 8 关:</strong> 需要达到 A+ 评分。<strong>(完整版可用)</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第 12 关:</strong> 仅限 S+ 评分玩家解锁，证明你已掌握所有前面关卡。<strong>(完整版可用)</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>合作多人模式 &amp; 单人模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以单独挑战，也可以与好友一起合作。制定策略、分享技巧、一起积累积分，加快你的进度。无论是单人模式还是合作模式，挑战都是真实的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/7903fb92e770098a9317974096b29139.poster.avif?t=1742134340\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/7903fb92e770098a9317974096b29139.webm?t=1742134340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/7903fb92e770098a9317974096b29139.mp4?t=1742134340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>连跳 &amp; 竞速机制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Git Gud</i> 的核心是 **连跳（Bunny Hopping）机制**，它对通关和高分挑战至关重要。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按住跳跃键可以自动连跳，并在移动时加速。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >连续跳跃六次后，你可以解锁 **二段跳**，这是完成高难度关卡和提升表现的关键技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/173186cdfbae2a7e9ef41f2f179a341c.poster.avif?t=1742134340\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/173186cdfbae2a7e9ef41f2f179a341c.webm?t=1742134340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/173186cdfbae2a7e9ef41f2f179a341c.mp4?t=1742134340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>竞速 &amp; 计时系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <i>Git Gud</i> 里，每一秒都至关重要。内置计时器会记录你在每个关卡的 **最佳成绩（PB）**。挑战自我，打破记录，冲上排行榜！如果你能进入前十名，你的名字将向全世界展示。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/6e85b7d0f7a5e7a7177c3812f2a118b4.poster.avif?t=1742134340\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/6e85b7d0f7a5e7a7177c3812f2a118b4.webm?t=1742134340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/6e85b7d0f7a5e7a7177c3812f2a118b4.mp4?t=1742134340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义 &amp; QR（快速重试）点数</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏开始时，你使用默认服装和轨迹，通过游戏玩法赚取 QR 点数，解锁新物品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QR 点数根据你的表现获得——挑战高等级关卡和更高分数将获得更高奖励。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合作模式中，当队友通关时，你也能获得额外 QR 点数！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QR 点数不仅仅用于商店购买道具——它们是快速重试和挑战高难度关卡的重要资源。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次重试都会消耗 QR 点数，如果用完了，你必须回到第 1 关重新积累。随着游戏难度的增加，重试成本也会提高，因此合理管理 QR 点数至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/2bf79a1e82371bc0fabf2508a4937e12.poster.avif?t=1742134340\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/2bf79a1e82371bc0fabf2508a4937e12.webm?t=1742134340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/2bf79a1e82371bc0fabf2508a4937e12.mp4?t=1742134340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tryhard 模式：高风险，高回报</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有信心吗？消耗 200 QR 点数激活 **Tryhard 模式**，在 15 分钟内，通关关卡的 QR 点数奖励将 **翻倍**！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但请注意——在此模式下，重试成本也会翻倍。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合理利用 Tryhard 模式，在你熟练掌握的关卡中高效赚取 QR 点数！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/b4d1ae616f96be4129619dd2d2f5c397.poster.avif?t=1742134340\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/b4d1ae616f96be4129619dd2d2f5c397.webm?t=1742134340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305620/extras/b4d1ae616f96be4129619dd2d2f5c397.mp4?t=1742134340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>准备 Git Gud 吧！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Git Gud</i> 将考验你的耐心，暴露你的策略漏洞，但每一次胜利都会让你感觉无比自豪。准备好冲击 S+ 评分，证明你的实力了吗？跳起来，Git Gud！</p>",
